          <name>Highway 1 (TransCanada Highway), in both directions. Maintenance planned between Perry River Bridge and Highway 23 South for 40.6 km (26 km east of Sicamous to Revelstoke). Starting Wed Apr 1 until Sun Jun 14. From 5:00 AM to 6:00 PM PST daily. Watch for traffic control personnel. Weed control works. Watch for slow moving vehicles on shoulder. Last updated Thu Feb 26 at 4:00 PM PST. (DBC-87863)</name>
