          <name>Highway 23, in both directions. Maintenance planned between Junction Highway 1 and Mica Dam for 149.9 km (Revelstoke). Starting Wed Apr 1 until Sun Jun 14. From 5:00 AM to 6:00 PM PST daily. Watch for traffic control personnel. Weed control works. Watch for slow moving vehicles on shoulder. Last updated Thu Feb 26 at 4:04 PM PST. (DBC-87873)</name>
