        <Placemark>
          <name>Highway 1 (TransCanada Highway), in both directions. Avalanche control work between Townley St and Anderson Rd for 141.4 km (Revelstoke to 1 km west of Golden). Road open to traffic. Road may close at anytime due to changing weather and avalanche conditions. Road is scheduled to close from 6am-8pm Thursday. Travelers are recommended to plan an alternate route. Next update time Thu Mar 19 at 5:00 AM PDT. Last updated Wed Mar 18 at 3:49 PM PDT. (DBC-88791)</name>
