        <Placemark>
          <name>[Truncated] Highway 1 (TransCanada Highway). Rest area closure planned at Highway 23 South (Revelstoke). Starting Wed Apr 1 until Sat Oct 31. The Revelstoke Rest Area will be closed due to highway upgrades in the area.
Nearby rest areas that remain open: Illecillewaet Break check rest area (Commercial and passenger vehicles), Rutherford rest area (Passenger vehicles), Shelter Bay rest area (Passenger vehicles) and The Last Spike rest area (commercial and passenger vehicles). Last updated Wed Mar</name>
