          <name>[Truncated] Highway 1 (TransCanada Highway), in both directions. Avalanche control work planned at Malakwa Rd (17 km east of Sicamous). Starting Thu Mar 19 at 5:00 AM PDT until Thu Mar 19 at 8:00 PM PDT. Industrial traffic may slow or block regular traffic. Watch for traffic control personnel. Eastbound commercial vehicles will be held in Malakwa for the duration of the Revelstoke to Golden closure. Eastbound passenger vehicles can bypass via Frontage Rd. Next update time Thu Mar 19 at 8:00 PM P</name>
