          <name>Highway 1 (TransCanada Highway), in both directions. Weather advisory in effect between Old Sicamous Rd and BC/Alberta Border for 291.1 km (Sicamous to 16 km east of Field). Elevated Avalanche conditions until Friday (March 20th) evening from Revelstoke to BC/AB Border. Travelers should expect extended closures for avalanche control and deposit removal. Consider alternate travel plans. Next update time Fri Mar 20 at 4:00 PM PDT. Last updated Tue Mar 17 at 1:26 PM PDT. (DBC-88789)</name>
