        <name>Cable Ferries</name>
        <Placemark>
          <name>Adam's Lake Cable Ferry</name>
          <description>
        &lt;![CDATA[
        &lt;h3&gt;🚢 Adam's Lake Cable Ferry&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Adams Lake ferry runs across Adams Lake, 20km north of Highway 1 between Chase and Sorrento. The ferry is located approximately 80km northeast of Kamloops and 50km northwest of Salmon Arm.&lt;/p&gt;
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Vessel Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Name:&lt;/b&gt; Unnamed&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Vehicle Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 10&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Passenger Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 48&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Crossing Time:&lt;/b&gt; 6 minutes&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Weight Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 34000 kg&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Schedule Type:&lt;/b&gt; On Demand 24hr With Gaps&lt;br/&gt;
            
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Schedule Information&lt;/h4&gt;
        Service hours:  On demand, 24-hours  5:00 am &amp;ndash; 3:00 am 3:00 am &amp;ndash; 5:00 am (emergency only)
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Contact Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Organization:&lt;/b&gt; WaterBridge Ferries Inc.&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 2502652105&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Live Webcams&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/1102.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/1095.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/1094.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last Updated:&lt;/b&gt; 2026-03-18T16:00:32.424894-07:00&lt;/p&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/transportation/passenger-travel/water-travel/inland-ferries/adams-lake-cable-ferry&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;More Information&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        ]]&gt;
        </description>
          <styleUrl>#style_FERRY_CABLE</styleUrl>
          <Point>
