        </Placemark>
        <Placemark>
          <name>Arrow Park Cable Ferry</name>
          <description>
        &lt;![CDATA[
        &lt;h3&gt;🚢 Arrow Park Cable Ferry&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Arrow Park ferry runs across the junction of Upper and Lower Arrow Lakes at Arrow Park, 22km south of Nakusp on Highway 6.&lt;/p&gt;
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Vessel Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Name:&lt;/b&gt; Unnamed&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Vehicle Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 24&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Passenger Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 48&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Crossing Time:&lt;/b&gt; 5 minutes&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Weight Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 141400 kg&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Schedule Type:&lt;/b&gt; On Demand Morning to Evening With Gaps&lt;br/&gt;
            
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Schedule Information&lt;/h4&gt;
        Service hours:  On demand  5:00 am &amp;ndash; 12:05 pm 2:15 pm &amp;ndash; 9:20 pm
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Contact Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Organization:&lt;/b&gt; WaterBridge Ferries Inc.&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 2502652105&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Live Webcams&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/1049.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/1048.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/1050.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last Updated:&lt;/b&gt; 2026-03-18T16:00:32.440311-07:00&lt;/p&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/transportation/passenger-travel/water-travel/inland-ferries/arrow-park-cable-ferry&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;More Information&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        ]]&gt;
        </description>
