        <Placemark>
          <name>Glade Cable Ferry</name>
          <description>
        &lt;![CDATA[
        &lt;h3&gt;🚢 Glade Cable Ferry&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Glade cable ferry runs across the Kootenay River on Highway 3A (22.5 kilometres west of Nelson) to Glade.&lt;/p&gt;
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Vessel Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Name:&lt;/b&gt; Unnamed&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Vehicle Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 10&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Passenger Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 48&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Crossing Time:&lt;/b&gt; 3 minutes&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Weight Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 63500 kg&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Schedule Type:&lt;/b&gt; On Demand Morning to Night&lt;br/&gt;
            
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Schedule Information&lt;/h4&gt;
        Service hours:  On demand  5:00 am &amp;ndash; 2:20 am
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Contact Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Organization:&lt;/b&gt; Western Pacific Marine&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 2502295650&lt;br/&gt;
        
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last Updated:&lt;/b&gt; 2026-03-18T16:00:32.415259-07:00&lt;/p&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/transportation/passenger-travel/water-travel/inland-ferries/glade-cable-ferry&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;More Information&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        ]]&gt;
        </description>
