          <Point>
            <coordinates>-117.54451545,49.39523552,0</coordinates>
          </Point>
        </Placemark>
        <Placemark>
          <name>Harrop Cable Ferry</name>
          <description>
        &lt;![CDATA[
        &lt;h3&gt;🚢 Harrop Cable Ferry&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Harrop ferry runs across Kootenay River, on Highway 3A, 24.5 kilometres northeast of Nelson and 8 kilometres west of Balfour to the communities of Harrop and Procter (on the south bank).&lt;/p&gt;
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Vessel Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Name:&lt;/b&gt; Unnamed&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Vehicle Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 24&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Passenger Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 98&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Crossing Time:&lt;/b&gt; 5 minutes&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Weight Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 141400 kg&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Schedule Type:&lt;/b&gt; On Demand 24hr&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Special Restrictions:&lt;/b&gt; Maximum weight per vehicle is 118,000kg.&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Schedule Information&lt;/h4&gt;
        Service hours:  On demand  24 hours
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Contact Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Organization:&lt;/b&gt; Western Pacific Marine&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 2502295650&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Live Webcams&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/569.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/567.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a href='https://images.drivebc.ca/bchighwaycam/pub/cameras/570.jpg' target='_blank'&gt;Webcam 3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last Updated:&lt;/b&gt; 2026-03-18T16:00:32.450427-07:00&lt;/p&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/transportation/passenger-travel/water-travel/inland-ferries/harrop-cable-ferry&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;More Information&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        ]]&gt;
        </description>
          <styleUrl>#style_FERRY_CABLE</styleUrl>
          <Point>
            <coordinates>-117.05404618,49.60942702,0</coordinates>
