        </Placemark>
        <Placemark>
          <name>Usk Reaction Ferry</name>
          <description>
        &lt;![CDATA[
        &lt;h3&gt;🚢 Usk Reaction Ferry&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Usk ferry runs across the Skeena River, about 16 kilometres northeast of Terrace, 0.8 kilometres off Highway 16, between South and North Usk.&lt;/p&gt;
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Vessel Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Name:&lt;/b&gt; Unnamed&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Vehicle Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 2&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Passenger Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 12&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Crossing Time:&lt;/b&gt; 7 minutes&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Weight Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; N/A kg&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Schedule Type:&lt;/b&gt; On Demand Morning to Night With Gaps&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Special Restrictions:&lt;/b&gt; Ferry capacity is 10 tonnes GVW and 12 passengers, including drivers. Vessel can carry 2 vehicles or 1 vehicle combination which cannot exceed 12 metres.&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Schedule Information&lt;/h4&gt;
        Service hours:  On demand  6:45 am &amp;ndash; 10:00 am 11:00 am &amp;ndash; 2:45 pm 3:15 pm &amp;ndash; 7:00 pm 8:00 pm &amp;ndash; 11:15 pm
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Contact Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Organization:&lt;/b&gt; Emil Anderson Maintenance&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 2506381881&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Alt Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 18006655051&lt;br/&gt;
        
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last Updated:&lt;/b&gt; 2026-03-18T16:00:32.467810-07:00&lt;/p&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/transportation/passenger-travel/water-travel/inland-ferries/usk-reaction-ferry&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;More Information&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        ]]&gt;
        </description>
          <styleUrl>#style_FERRY_ON_DEMAND</styleUrl>
          <Point>
            <coordinates>-128.40987785,54.63541178,0</coordinates>
          </Point>
        </Placemark>
        <Placemark>
          <name>Little Fort Reaction Ferry</name>
          <description>
        &lt;![CDATA[
        &lt;h3&gt;🚢 Little Fort Reaction Ferry&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Little Fort ferry runs across the North Thompson River, 93 kilometres north of Kamloops on Highway 5.&lt;/p&gt;
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Vessel Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Name:&lt;/b&gt; Unnamed&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Vehicle Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 2&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Passenger Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 12&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Crossing Time:&lt;/b&gt; 5 minutes&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Weight Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; N/A kg&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Schedule Type:&lt;/b&gt; On Demand Morning to Evening With Gaps&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Special Restrictions:&lt;/b&gt; Maximum carrying capacity 9 tonnes, approximately 2 passenger vehicles. Vehicle combination cannot exceed 12m.&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Schedule Information&lt;/h4&gt;
        Service hours:  On demand  7:00 am &amp;ndash; noon 1:00 pm &amp;ndash; 6:20 pm
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Contact Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Organization:&lt;/b&gt; Argo Road Maintenance Inc.&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 2503746690&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Alt Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 18006612025&lt;br/&gt;
        
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last Updated:&lt;/b&gt; 2026-03-18T16:00:32.491298-07:00&lt;/p&gt;
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content/transportation/passenger-travel/water-travel/inland-ferries/little-fort-reaction-ferry&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;More Information&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
        ]]&gt;
        </description>
