        <Placemark>
          <name>Lytton Reaction Ferry</name>
          <description>
        &lt;![CDATA[
        &lt;h3&gt;🚢 Lytton Reaction Ferry&lt;/h3&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;The Lytton ferry runs across the Fraser River, about 2.4 kilometres north of Lytton.&lt;/p&gt;
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Vessel Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Name:&lt;/b&gt; Unnamed&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Vehicle Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 2&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Passenger Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; 18&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Crossing Time:&lt;/b&gt; 5 minutes&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Weight Capacity:&lt;/b&gt; N/A kg&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Schedule Type:&lt;/b&gt; On Demand 24hr With Gaps&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Special Restrictions:&lt;/b&gt; Maximum carrying capacity 9 tonnes, approximately 2 passenger vehicles. Vehicle combination cannot exceed 12m.&lt;br/&gt;
        
        &lt;h4&gt;Schedule Information&lt;/h4&gt;
        Service hours:On demand  6:30 am &amp;ndash; 8:45 am 9:00 am &amp;ndash; 10:30 am 11:00 am &amp;ndash; 12:45 pm 1:00 pm &amp;ndash; 4:30 pm 4:45 pm &amp;ndash; 6:30 pm 7:00 pm &amp;ndash; 8:45 pm 9:00 pm &amp;ndash; 12:30 am 12:45 am &amp;ndash; 2:30 am 3:00 am &amp;ndash; 4:45 am 5:00 am &amp;ndash; 6:30 am
        
        
            &lt;h4&gt;Contact Information&lt;/h4&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Organization:&lt;/b&gt; Yellowhead Road &amp; Bridge (Nicola) Ltd.&lt;br/&gt;
            &lt;b&gt;Alt Phone:&lt;/b&gt; 18888999854&lt;br/&gt;&lt;b&gt;Email:&lt;/b&gt; &lt;a href='mailto:nicola@yrb.ca'&gt;nicola@yrb.ca&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Last Updated:&lt;/b&gt; 2026-03-18T16:00:32.361113-07:00&lt;/p&gt;
        
